{"tid":1614395,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【和理非新戰術】鎖鏈技能樹升階指南！","createTime":"2019-10-02T18:38:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T13:11:59.000Z","uid":127735,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c5fe79e2c1a00a470a6aabd204b3e6d46a73c32c","tid":1614395,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:38:47.000Z","msg":"鑑於另一個Post，見到鎖鏈技能極之有效，爭取到好多隊友撤退既時間，而且成本低之餘，更重要既係我地可以預先佈防，係撤退方面，同火系魔法有同曲異工之妙處<br />\n<br />\n已解鎖技能：鎖鏈結界<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1614060\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1614060</a><br />\n<br />\n但鑑於敵人試過一次之後，將來一定會大攜工具黎破解，所以教大家如何走分支路線或走單一升級路線應付各種場合，首先介紹一下分支系列：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">火系</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n火系適用於敵方唔鎖閘或唔落閘，將中門大開之時。若見閘門未鎖，可預先將一大筒易燃性液體倒於閘內，當敵軍衝上，一支酒即事成！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">毒系</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n毒系適用於敵方已鎖閘門之時。先對閘門施放原有鎖鏈技能，其後將大量腐蝕性液體倒於閘各鎖鏈上，但該技能需提醒隊友勿觸摸中毒！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">油系</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n油系於各種場合亦適用，但平地效果較低，於有樓梯位置愈長梯級則加成愈多，其利處係可配合上述兩系技能一齊使用。於閘前或樓梯位置倒上大量油性液體即可成事！<br />\n<br />\n跟住就係<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">鎖鏈技能樹精通技能</span></strong>：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">首尾呼應</span></strong>：<br />\n較易習得，於閘最上及最下位置施放鎖鏈技能，令敵方消耗更多時間！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">連環緊扣</span></strong>：<br />\n較易習得，施放多次鎖鏈技能，並互相混亂緊扣！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">自動鎖鏈</span></strong>：<br />\n習得成本較大，運用裝備，將鎮鏈技能自動施放！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LsC7OvAFq8w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLsC7OvAFq8w&d=ualpl%2FmkMQCwG5JKQRKj7F%2BSpyvFQ8bIEt1ajTFSrzY%3D&h=874285e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LsC7OvAFq8w</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">碎星枷鎖</span></strong>：<br />\n習得容易，需碎石消耗品，於閘門隙縫間放置碎石，使閘門較難推開！<br />\n<br />\n以上技能為睇片及見Post心得後合集，如有額外技能請係下面加上<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：玩緊鎖鏈既手遊"},{"pid":"08f4f45c256f6aa410736fb3bdc8713a125670fe","tid":1614395,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:39:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b74259a4772d60c2422ab3e56ec4eb46a775b7e0","tid":1614395,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:39:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d29a0a12383e9ac6a1906c963705076a7c438663","tid":1614395,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:40:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a7a6f65a9d6d1cdfc7e9bedfbb9f8a7ec36f74bd","tid":1614395,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:40:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b9f788f2f937ba16e5b25801bcc78623eaa0b37c","tid":1614395,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:41:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55a09fe9d95b67807a1a72b5cd269d3b984d35f6","tid":1614395,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:41:21.000Z","msg":"咁夜出Post，推唔推到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2ef56814c76b47ec38e10c4ec18d77f2d61616f","tid":1614395,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:41:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bc7f31c6ea598a080141e45f8fa89beb4ce992a","tid":1614395,"uid":127735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"55a09fe9d95b67807a1a72b5cd269d3b984d35f6","tid":1614395,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:41:21.000Z","msg":"咁夜出Post，推唔推到架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:41:38.000Z","msg":"夜晚先唸到野嘛"},{"pid":"ed9ff5af23a008c6bbe593f6c4589174060b7130","tid":1614395,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T18:41:38.000Z","msg":"幫推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agr